        <title>Blue shift &amp; Opp. Force</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[danielsangeo]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>In the games’ <a href="https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=1040-JWMT-2947" data-bbcode="true">launch options in Steam</a>, add this:</p>
<p>-w 1280 -h 800</p>
<p>If that doesn’t work, you’re not going to be able to do it for the reason deathparade mentioned (and remove the -w and -h commands from the launch options so you can still play the games in the provided resolutions).</p>
